{"tid":1643383,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[緊急] 黨鐵CCTV 有人面辨識功能","createTime":"2019-10-10T05:58:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-15T05:43:24.000Z","uid":3145,"like":20,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"626c46b71ca2de24160634407e1740480a33f7a3","tid":1643383,"uid":3145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T05:58:46.000Z","msg":"網上流傳緊 有前線員工爆料閂站裝呢舊野<br />\n而裝嘅位置係車廂入面<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UwMD6Ta.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUwMD6Ta.jpg&h=afdef5a7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁作為一個工程撚 見舊嘢都幾奇怪<br />\n上黨鐵網望望佢之前出嘅tender<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.mtr.com.hk/en/corporate/tenders/PQ063254.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mtr.com.hk%2Fen%2Fcorporate%2Ftenders%2FPQ063254.html&d=N3SWmacea4shigR4hA2EmxPkB4X9Hpa20B1QJvXseFg%3D&h=5f62e891\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.mtr.com.hk/en/corporate/tenders/PQ063254.html</a><br />\n見到其中一段咁嘅文字<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RVgdbjR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRVgdbjR.jpg&h=8d2f18b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n&middot;     Security System &ndash; assessment and application of AI facial recognition function on CCTV, enhancing crisis management, access control or tenant registration system by using the latest technology;<br />\n<br />\n原來張tender 入面 保安系統<br />\n黨鐵要應用CCTV 嘅人面辨識功能<br />\n<br />\nInterested companies should register in writing to Procurement &amp; Contracts Department at 20/F., MTR Headquarters Building, Telford Plaza, Kowloon Bay, Kowloon, Hong Kong on/before 2:00pm on 20 July 2018 together with the following information for prequalification:-<br />\n<br />\n回覆時間係7月20號前 而家裝緊時間上都幾合理<br />\n係咪真事 香港人自己識分析<br />\n你哋係咪仲要再搭佢呢？<br />\n<br />\n和理非們 咪撚搭啦<br />\n勇武們 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"